	* Kafka consummer for Storm. This code is forked
	Thomas Becker https://github.com/wurstmeister. Buldoop 
	uses this Storm spout for connect kafka (bus layer) with
	the speed layer (in this case with Storm).
	This first package version is based on the master branch,
	freeze with a commit hash.
